sys_hub_action_type_definition.annotation: Find difference between two datetime objects
sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Compares two date/time objects.
Returns difference in various formats.
If only one date/time is submitted, the other date/time is set as system current date/time.
Return values are always zero or positive integer values. Taken from Share: by Ola Norlander https://developer.servicenow.com/connect.do#!/share/contents/6377513_date_difference_in_flow_designer?v=1&t=PRODUCT_DETAILS
sys_hub_action_type_definition.name: Date Compare
